  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">"🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — Q7 scope expansion; large component suite; UX-critical."</step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">Read TASK-INDEX; confirm 065 + 069 complete.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">Read SPAARKEAI-DASHBOARD-AND-WIDGET-MODEL + Fluent v9 patterns + IPinnedContextService API.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Add BFF Endpoint Pair">`GET /api/memory/pinned`, `POST /api/memory/pinned`, `PUT /api/memory/pinned/{id}`, `DELETE /api/memory/pinned/{id}` per ADR-008 + ADR-016. Register in existing module.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Build PinnedMemoryListWidget">Context-pane widget; groups by pinType; filter + search.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Build PinnedMemoryEditDialog">Fluent v9 dialog; controlled form; validation.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Build PinnedMemoryDeleteConfirmation">Confirmation dialog with cross-session impact warning.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Build PinnedMemoryProvenanceBadge">Source attribution badge.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Register with ContextWidgetRegistry">List widget registered.</step>
    <step order="9" name="Light/Dark Parity Audit">ADR-021 audit on every component; capture screenshots.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-008/010/012/013/021/029/030).</step>
    <step order="10" name="UI Tests + Integration Test">Per ui-test skill: each component renders correctly + functional flows work + dark mode passes. Integration test: voice-command-created items appear in UI + UI-created items appear in subsequent chat session memory composition.</step>
    <step order="11" name="Document + Complete">TASK-INDEX 070 ✅. Q7 expansion status noted.</step>
  </steps>

