  <notes>
    <note>**Q7 SCOPE EXPANSION**: This task represents the single largest Phase C frontend deliverable. Original spec.md Q7 deferred full memory UI to R7; owner approved expansion to R6 on 2026-06-07. Adds 1-2 weeks to Phase C calendar. Re-defer fallback per plan.md risk R4.</note>
